        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "WATCH THE VIDEO: Once on paper, the ink appears fully legible and undiscernable from a normal pen for 15 minutes but slowly starts to disappear; fading within 20-30 minutes; completely after about an hour",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "REALLY WORKS: Looks like a real pen with no markings to distinquish it otherwise. Nine out of ten times, you might pick this pen out of a cup of many; it looks like a pen you would want to use; Magicians, spys and secrects oh my",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "WRITING CAPACITY: Invisible formula ball point pen will write up to 2500 feet before running out of ink; lots of use and entertainment for all ages",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "SPECIFICATIONS: Fine Point; Size: 0.5mm; Ink Color: Blue; Pen Case: Clear",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
